    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2272860/extras/f09f3d3a341e4fc1573ce77d045c804b.poster.avif?t=1744286628\" width=642 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2272860/extras/f09f3d3a341e4fc1573ce77d045c804b.webm?t=1744286628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2272860/extras/f09f3d3a341e4fc1573ce77d045c804b.mp4?t=1744286628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Rogue Tank is a chaotic 3D tank shooter with rogue-lite elements. Enter the arena with your trusty tank. It’s time to wreak havoc!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COMBINE DEADLY UPGRADES</h2>Upgrade your tank as you defeat your enemies. Pick upgrades that fit your style of combat. However, choose carefully, as combining the right set of upgrades will turn your tank into an absolute force of destruction.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2272860/extras/709df50891075ff6d2ea7a65408156d1.avif?t=1744286628\" width=620 height=320 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WIELD THE TOOLS OF DESTRUCTION</h2>Bombard enemies with your turret, crash them into deadly arena traps, zap them with lightning, or burn them to a crisp. Destroy your enemies with a diverse set of tools as you dodge incoming attacks.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2272860/extras/9544d290575cc88bed700e0b216943cb.poster.avif?t=1744286628\" width=644 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2272860/extras/9544d290575cc88bed700e0b216943cb.webm?t=1744286628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2272860/extras/9544d290575cc88bed700e0b216943cb.mp4?t=1744286628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UNLOCK AND REPLAY</h2>Unlock new weapons, upgrades, and arenas as you battle. Permanently upgrade your tank to become even stronger!",
